      "actionDate": "2025-07-10",
      "actionDesc": "Reported to House",
      "text": "<p><strong>Syria Terrorism Threat Assessment Act</strong></p><p>This bill requires the Department of Homeland Security to provide Congress with an assessment of terrorist threats to the United States posed by individuals in Syria affiliated with either a foreign terrorist organization or a specially designated global terrorist organization.</p>",
